Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.49,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)}Uma suave nevasca de lembrança
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.76,0:00:04.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Ei, ei, ei! Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He isn't here}Oh? Ele não está aqui?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.51,0:00:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ele está ligando para você.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, this isn't good. Without thinking, I...}O-Oh, eu não poderia mostrar meu rosto agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's enough}Quero dizer! Saia já!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{}Se você não sair, eu vou te dar uma surra!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.06,0:00:35.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos acabar com você!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você sabe onde está o Usopp, Sogeking?\NNão consigo encontrá-lo em lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.99,0:00:45.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He went back ahead of us on a small boat earlier.\N}D-Não se preocupe.\NEle partiu em um pequeno barco, pouco antes de nós.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{..}Mas esta nave na verdade pertence a ele agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.40,0:00:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just what is it they need in \Norder to recognize Usopp?\N}Como diabos eles não reconhecem que ele é o Usopp?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui também não.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.64,0:01:10.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As we suspected, I can't find anyone anywhere on this ship.\N}É como pensamos.\NNão há ninguém em nenhum lugar deste navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é estranho.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder who on earth sailed this ship to us...}Eu me pergunto quem poderia ter conduzido este navio até nós.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But we definitely heard that \Nvoice calling out to us.\N}Mas todos ouvimos a mesma voz nos chamando.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that right?}Você fez?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, alguém certamente nos chamou.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.14,0:01:28.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like I said all this time...\N\Nit was the Merry's voice!\N}Como venho dizendo, era a voz do Merry!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.40,0:01:31.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que?! Realmente?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.57,0:01:36.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, Feliz?! Dizer algo!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{w}Seu idiota. Não há como uma nave falar.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.80,0:01:44.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I kinda felt that way too, though...}Eu meio que me senti assim no começo,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.11,0:01:49.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But there's no way something like that... could happen, huh?}mas algo assim deveria ser impossível, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see a ship coming towards us!}Há um navio vindo em nossa direção!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Quem é aquele?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.74,0:02:07.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão vivos!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vocês estão bem!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Galley-La Company's ship...}Um navio da Companhia Galley-La?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é incrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.16,0:02:16.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They rushed out in Aqua Laguna and still made it okay!\NI can't believe it!\N}Eles saíram correndo no meio do Aqua Laguna e ainda assim conseguiram!\NEu não posso acreditar!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles voltaram do Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{!}Olá, Iceboss!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{..}Estúpido-burgo.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{..}Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que grupo louco.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles enfrentaram o Governo Mundial...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{they }e realmente recuperei tudo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alegre!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{ is...}Olhar! O navio deles!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que está acontecendo?!\NO que aconteceu de repente?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{this just}De repente? Não é natural?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was declared that Merry could no longer sail.}O Merry foi declarado impróprio para o mar.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...}Mas!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The }Alegre!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pops}Chefe!\NIsso é ruim!\NFeliz está com problemas!\NVocê tem que fazer alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys...\NThis is good timing!\NYou guys're all shipwrights, right?!\N}Pessoal, este é um ótimo momento!\NVocês são todos construtores navais, certo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estou te implorando! Por favor, faça alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's our friend who has been traveling with us all this time!}Ela é nossa amiga e viaja conosco há muito tempo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E há pouco ela nos salvou!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{pops}Então, por favor, chefe!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then let her...}Então permita que ela...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{}descansar agora.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já fiz tudo que pude.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.57,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{this}Que som é esse?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.36,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Alguém está na Scrap Island?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.47,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{...}Este não é o navio dos Chapéus de Palha?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.38,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The damage must've been caused by Aqua Laguna. It's in a terrible state.}Os danos do Aqua Laguna a deixaram em péssimo estado.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.88,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Well, I guess it's beyond just damage...}Não, ela era assim antes da tempestade.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.84,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Eu quero zarpar.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.06,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,O que é que foi isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.31,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Quero zarpar pela última vez!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.27,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,O que estou fazendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.51,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{..}Não há mais esperança para este navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.18,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Iceburg-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.74,0:05:36.73,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo aí?!\NOutra grande onda está chegando!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.62,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.09,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,O que?! Você quer zarpar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.05,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The sea is still stormy!}A tempestade ainda não passou!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.31,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Irei sozinho se for preciso.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,O que?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.36,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{We can't let you go out there all by yourself!}Então não podemos deixar você sair sozinho!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{watching}Estou testemunhando um milagre agora:
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A miracle of a ship that has long passed its limits...\N}O milagre de um navio que há muito ultrapassou os seus limites.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been a shipwright for many years,}Em todos os meus anos como construtor naval,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I've never seen \Na pirate ship this incredible.\N}Nunca vi um navio pirata tão notável.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's lived a splendid life.}Ela viveu uma vida esplêndida.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.97,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Let's go back, everyone!}Pessoal, vamos voltar!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.91,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,De volta aos mares da aventura!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.15,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Alegre!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Eu vim pegar você!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Entendo.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, then... are you guys ready?}Pois bem, vocês estão prontos?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Merry... the seabed is dark and lonesome,}Feliz, o fundo do mar é escuro e solitário,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so we'll watch you to the end.}então nos veremos até o fim.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{ was good}Talvez seja melhor que Usopp não esteja aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem como... ele aguentar isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Alguma ideia?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Discordo.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos um dia deverão dizer adeus.\NEsta é a separação de um homem.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Not even a single tear should be shed.}Não devo derramar uma única lágrima.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He, too... is prepared.}Então ele também está preparado.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.15,0:09:44.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for carrying us for \Nsuch a long time, Merry.\N}Você nos carregou por tanto tempo.\NObrigado, Feliz.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...}Neve!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.99,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Uma caravela!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.63,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.46,0:10:20.80,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Agora o navio pirata, o Going Merry, está completo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.80,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Felicidades ao nosso novo navio e companheiro de tripulação!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Look at this!\N\NThe Merry got damaged quite a bit!\N}Veja isso!\NO Merry sofreu bastante dano!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.24,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{When navigating a sailboat, \Neveryone has to participate!\N}Ao operar um navio a vela, cada um precisa fazer a sua parte!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.00,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Learn it appropriately!}Você precisa se lembrar disso!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.00,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhora.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.37,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Eu sou Shoree.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.43,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?!}O que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.52,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Prática de canhão!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.25,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{}Eles com certeza não voam muito bem!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Estou lhe dizendo, deixe-me tentar!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.92,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Incrível! Você acertou na primeira tentativa!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.64,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{...}Uau! Eu realmente acertei na minha primeira tentativa!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.39,0:11:20.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Ei! Esse é o meu lugar!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The entrance to the Grand Line \Nlies ahead of that light.\N}A entrada da Grand Line fica logo além daquela luz.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.12,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Para encontrar o All Blue!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Para ser o rei dos piratas!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.79,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Para se tornar o maior espadachim!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.55,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Para desenhar um mapa mundial!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.00,0:11:43.26,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}T-Para se tornar um bravo guerreiro do mar!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.66,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{We're going...}Vamos para a Grande Linha!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,A entrada da Grand Line é uma montanha!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.99,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Uma montanha?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.55,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Nós conseguimos!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.68,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Este é o maior mar do mundo!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.41,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Go}Continue!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.50,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{}Estamos voando para fora disso!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.91,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{going}Não olhe para trás!\NSeguimos em frente!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.59,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me juntar-me à sua tripulação.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.92,0:13:11.20,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Não tenho para onde ir e nenhum lugar para chamar de lar.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.42,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Então deixe-me ficar neste navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.92,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{..}Oh, eu vejo. Então acho que não temos escolha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.50,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.48,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.53,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Quem é o navegador deste navio?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.49,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Estamos voando!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.49,0:13:28.68,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Incrível! O navio está voando!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.41,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{a }É a Ilha do Céu!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...}Desculpe;
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu queria levar você ainda mais longe.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...}Desculpe;
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to continue going on \Nadventures with you forever.\N}Eu queria compartilhar aventuras com você para sempre.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alegre!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...}Uma voz!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eu–
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.18,0:15:30.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's us who have to apologize, Merry!}Somos nós que precisamos nos desculpar, Merry!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...}Eu não sou bom em dirigir,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so I ran you into icebergs at times...}então às vezes eu batia com você em icebergs.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There was a time I tore the sails, too.}Uma vez também rasguei suas velas!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.27,0:15:46.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Zoro and Sanji are stupid, \Nso they broke all sorts of things!\N}Zoro e Sanji agem como estúpidos juntos, então eles quebraram todo tipo de coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp would fix them each time, \Nbut he isn't good at it!\N}Usopp sempre consertava você, mas ele não era muito bom nisso!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So it's us who have to...}Então somos nós que precisamos nos desculpar!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas tenho estado feliz.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much...\N\Nfor taking good care of me all this time.\N}Muito obrigado por cuidar bem de mim todo esse tempo.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente tenho sido feliz...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,porque eu tive você.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.81,0:16:44.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alegre!
